;Programa principal: recebe a, b e c
; a indica a operação
; b e c são os operandos

READ R11 ;a
READ R2  ;b
READ R3  ;c

STORE R2 OPB
STORE R3 OPC

LOAD R7 AD
SUB R11 R7
JZ SOMA

ADD R11 R7
LOAD R7 SU
SUB R11 R7
JZ SUBTRAI

ADD R11 R7
LOAD R7 MU
SUB R11 R7
JZ MULTIPLICA

ADD R11 R7
LOAD R7 DI
SUB R11 R7
JZ DIVIDE

ADD R11 R7
LOAD R7 PO
SUB R11 R7
JZ POTENCIA

X: WORD 0
Y: WORD 1
AD: WORD 1
SU: WORD 2
MU: WORD 3
DI: WORD 4
PO: WORD 5

OPB:
OPC:
